## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="858c5-102"><xref:System.ArithmeticException> 是下列的例外狀況的基底類別：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-102"><xref:System.ArithmeticException> is the base class for the following exceptions:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="858c5-103"><xref:System.DivideByZeroException>其中中擲回整數除法除數為 0。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-103"><xref:System.DivideByZeroException>, which is thrown in integer division when the divisor is 0.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="858c5-104">例如，嘗試除以 10 由 0 則會擲回<xref:System.DivideByZeroException>例外狀況。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-104">For example, attempting to divide 10 by 0 throws a <xref:System.DivideByZeroException> exception.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="858c5-105"><xref:System.NotFiniteNumberException>它就會擲回時不會對作業，或傳回<xref:System.Double.NaN?displayProperty=nameWithType>， <xref:System.Double.NegativeInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>， <xref:System.Double.PositiveInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>， <xref:System.Single.NaN?displayProperty=nameWithType>， <xref:System.Single.NegativeInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>， <xref:System.Single.PositiveInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>，且使用的程式設計語言不支援這些值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-105"><xref:System.NotFiniteNumberException>, which is thrown when an operation is performed on or returns <xref:System.Double.NaN?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Double.NegativeInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Double.PositiveInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Single.NaN?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Single.NegativeInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Single.PositiveInfinity?displayProperty=nameWithType>, and the programming language used does not support those values.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="858c5-106"><xref:System.OverflowException>其會擲回作業的結果超出界限的目標資料類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-106"><xref:System.OverflowException>, which is thrown when the result of an operation is outside the bounds of the target data type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="858c5-107">也就是說，小於數字的`MinValue`屬性或大於其`MaxValue`屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-107">That is, it is less than a number's `MinValue` property or greater than its `MaxValue` property.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="858c5-108">例如，嘗試指派 200 + 200<xref:System.Byte>值會擲回<xref:System.OverflowException>例外狀況，因為 400 大於 256，上限<xref:System.Byte>資料型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-108">For example, attempting to assign 200 + 200 to a <xref:System.Byte> value throws an <xref:System.OverflowException> exception, since 400 greater than 256, the upper bound of the <xref:System.Byte> data type.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="858c5-109">您的程式碼不應該處理，或擲回這個例外狀況。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-109">Your code should not handle or throw this exception.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="858c5-110">相反地，您應該處理，或擲回其中一個其衍生的類別，因為它更精確地表示錯誤的確實性質。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-110">Instead, you should either handle or throw one of its derived classes, since it more precisely indicates the exact nature of the error.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="858c5-111">如需執行個體的初始屬性值的清單<xref:System.ArithmeticException>，請參閱<xref:System.ArithmeticException>建構函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-111">For a list of initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.ArithmeticException>, see the <xref:System.ArithmeticException> constructors.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="858c5-112"><xref:System.ArithmeticException> 會使用 HRESULT COR_E_ARITHMETIC，0x80070216 的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="858c5-112"><xref:System.ArithmeticException> uses the HRESULT COR_E_ARITHMETIC, which has the value 0x80070216.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
